---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout title="Variaveis de Ambiente - Documentacao" adm={true} activePage="/admin/docs">
  <div class="docs-layout">
    <aside class="docs-sidebar">
      <nav class="docs-nav">
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Getting Started</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs">Visao Geral</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/structure">Estrutura</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Sistema</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/auth">Autenticacao</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/store">Loja e Carrinho</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/ai">Inteligencia Artificial</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Backend</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/database">Banco de Dados</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/api">APIs</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Configuracao</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/env" class="active">Variaveis de Ambiente</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/commands">Comandos</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="docs-content">
      <h1><Icon name="lucide:settings-2" size={24} /> Variaveis de Ambiente</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        O projeto utiliza arquivos <code>.env</code> para configuracao. Copie
        <code>.env.example</code> para <code>.env</code> e preencha os valores.
      </p>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:lock" size={20} /> Autenticacao Owner</h2>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>ADMIN_OWNER_EMAIL</code>
        <span>Email do administrador para login</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>ADMIN_PASSWORD</code>
        <span>Senha do administrador (mínimo 8 caracteres)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>ADMIN_SESSION_SECRET</code>
        <span>Chave secreta para assinar tokens HMAC (minimo 32 caracteres)</span>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:database" size={20} /> Banco de Dados (Turso)</h2>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>TURSO_DATABASE_URL</code>
        <span>URL do banco Turso (libsql://seu-projeto.turso.io)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN</code>
        <span>Token de autenticacao do Turso</span>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:brain" size={20} /> Inteligencia Artificial</h2>
      <p>Configure pelo menos uma provedora de IA:</p>

      <div class="env-var">
        <code>OPENAI_API_KEY</code>
        <span>Chave da API da OpenAI (sk-...)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</code>
        <span>Chave da API da Anthropic (sk-ant-...)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>GEMINI_API_KEY</code>
        <span>Chave da API do Google Gemini (AIza...)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>MISTRAL_API_KEY</code>
        <span>Chave da API da Mistral</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>GROQ_API_KEY</code>
        <span>Chave da API da Groq (gsk_...)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>COHERE_API_KEY</code>
        <span>Chave da API da Cohere</span>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:mail" size={20} /> Email (Resend)</h2>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>RESEND_API_KEY</code>
        <span>Chave da API do Resend para envio de emails</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>RESEND_FROM_EMAIL</code>
        <span>Email de origem para envios (verified@seudominio.com)</span>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:server" size={20} /> Deployment (Vercel)</h2>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>HOST</code>
        <span>URL do host (definido automaticamente pelo Vercel)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="env-var">
        <code>ORIGIN</code>
        <span>URL de origem para CORS (https://seudominio.com)</span>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:file-text" size={20} /> Exemplo de .env</h2>
      <pre># Autenticacao
ADMIN_OWNER_EMAIL=admin@seudominio.com
ADMIN_PASSWORD=senha-segura-123
ADMIN_SESSION_SECRET=uma-chave-secreta-muito-longa-e-segura-32chars

# Banco de Dados
TURSO_DATABASE_URL=libsql://meu-projeto.turso.io
TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN=eyJh...

# IA (pelo menos uma)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...

# Email
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@seudominio.com

# Deployment
ORIGIN=https://seudominio.com</pre>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:alert-triangle" size={20} /> Seguranca</h2>
      <ul class="warning-list">
        <li>Nunca commite arquivos <code>.env</code> no git</li>
        <li>Adicione <code>.env</code> ao <code>.gitignore</code></li>
        <li>Use valores unicos para <code>ADMIN_SESSION_SECRET</code></li>
        <li>Em producao, configure as variaveis no painel do Vercel</li>
      </ul>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs-layout {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 70px auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .docs-sidebar {
    width: 260px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 90px;
    height: fit-content;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 110px);
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .docs-nav {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .docs-nav-section a {
    display: block;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-sm);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .docs-nav-section a:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-10);
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .docs-nav-section a.active {
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-20);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .docs-content {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .docs-content h1 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content h1 svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .docs-content h2 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary-alpha-20);
  }

  .docs-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .docs-content h2 svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .docs-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .docs-content p {
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content code {
    font-family: monospace;
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-10);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 0.2em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .docs-content pre {
    background: var(--color-gray-900);
    color: #f8f8f2;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .env-var {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.875rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .env-var code {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .env-var span {
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .warning-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .warning-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
  }

  .warning-list li::before {
    content: '!';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #f59e0b;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .docs-layout {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .docs-sidebar {
      width: 100%;
      position: static;
    }

    .docs-nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .env-var {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-nav,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h1,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h2 {
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content p,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .env-var span,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .warning-list li {
    color: #a0a0a0;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .env-var {
    background: #252525;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .warning-list li {
    border-color: #333;
  }
</style>
